<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Pi̱ki ʋba binili ma! ƲIT82</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<aka>Prayer for Divine Aid</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki ʋba binili ma!
 Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke;
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo keyukma,
 Nanta 'k osh pi̱ nukha̱kla wa.

[V2]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki Chihowa ma!
 Shilombish Holitopa ka
 Et ish pihi̱ma pulla na,
 Pi nuktaiyala pullashke.

[V3]
 Hatak ayoshoba puta
 Hʋpi yʋmohmi chatuk ʋt,
 Kanchi pi bʋnna fehna ka,
 Auet ish pi apelashke.

[V4]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki chia hoka,
 Himak a nitak okʋno
 Chim antia pi bʋnna hosh,
 Yakohmit e taloʋshke.

[V5]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki chia hokʋt,
 Auet ish pi apela na,
 Ish ai ahanta fehna ka
 E pihi̱sa mak inlashke.

[V6]
 Achukma bieka hocha
 Ʋm antia mak inlashke;
 Ish pim aiahni pullashke;
 Ʋba Pi̱ki Chihowa ma!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>82</hymn_number>
<author>Cyrus Byington</author>
</song>